      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the resistance thing and all but it just feels like a lot of unnecessary chemicals if the bacteria is already dead. most of the time i don't even need them. if the symptoms are 100% gone, isn't it basically just extra strain on my liver and kidneys for no reason? can't i just stop now and save my body the trouble?",
