      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see why the \"risk\" of a tiny few bacteria is worse than the known stress of taking meds for 7 more days. if i'm feeling perfect, it's a sign my body handled it. honestly, i've heard from people that you're supposed to stop as soon as symptoms disappear to keep your gut microbiome healthy. wouldn't stopping now actually be better for my overall health than just blindly following a 10-day rule?",
